{"tid":1935272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［灣仔區議會］ 民政署要求議員停止派發印有武漢肺炎字眼的防疫包","createTime":"2020-03-20T12:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T14:44:49.000Z","uid":22556,"like":11,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6141ab8553a33d3817fe409452ae82bbdc01f2ae","tid":1935272,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"〈民政署因為「武漢肺炎」￼擅阻灣仔區議會派發防疫包￼〉<br />\n<br />\n￼今日傍晚收到電郵￼，民政處突然指灣仔區議會早前印製的防疫包小冊子上面的「武漢肺炎」￼字眼不符世界衛生組織的名稱「2019冠狀病毒病￼￼」。￼<br />\n<br />\n小冊子是防疫包的重要部份，除了提供物資給有需要的市民，亦希望提醒他們注意日常衛生。民政署突然要求合辦團體停止派發，￼或採用衛生防護中心的單張，是多此一舉￼￼。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，￼單張內容並無問題，武漢肺炎亦是對此病毒的慣用名稱，民政署亦不能干預機構和由區議會通過的活動細節。即使停派必需由區議會通過，本人歡迎民政處將此項議程提交下星期二區議會大會討論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/901237633284250/posts/3612565185484801/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F901237633284250%2Fposts%2F3612565185484801%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=01d38b63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/901237633284250/posts/3612565185484801/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"0df8c346149ba70e13ecab8239a9caa4030c90a2","tid":1935272,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cbdcfb5de9010e2b905bca7b6e515e111365a9","tid":1935272,"uid":200550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13429d69c39d4f80dc1853ae6f05e0a91e08f386","tid":1935272,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"文字獄"},{"pid